long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
SETI Protect ensures that only your face can access your Chrome browser and the data within. Using advanced AI technology from Smart Eye Technology, it employs continuous facial tracking to authenticate your identity as you use your Chrome browser, protecting against remote desktop hacks, session jacking and phishing attacks.

Smart Eye Technology, Inc is the new leader in the bio-metrical multifactor authentication (MFA/2FA) cybersecurity arena. Leveraging a core set of verifications, continuous facial recognition, fingerprint, handwriting, and voice, SETI is only company designing frameworks of protection for based on you.
